Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the Fort de la Presentation Memorial Highway
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system constituting route 68 in the city of Ogdensburg, county of St. Lawrence, as the "Fort de la Presentation Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Fort de la Presentation Memorial Highway"
